# 3ds Max 🎮🧱

3ds Max is a professional 3D modeling, animation, and rendering software by Autodesk.

## 🚀 Features
- High-quality 3D modeling tools
- Animation and rigging support 🎬
- Powerful rendering options 🌟
- Large plugin and script ecosystem 🔧

## 🎯 Used For
- Game development 🎮
- Architectural visualization 🏙️
- Film and VFX production 🎥

## 💻 Platform
Available on **Windows**



